    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out with documented rationale consistent with ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 requirements at MRL 2. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory submission claim that worst-case hemolysis operating conditions are correctly identified, with RH < 1 confirmed at all five evaluated operating points. Medium assurance level is appropriate given medium model influence and high decision consequence at MRL 2.",
